'''Mushroom''' is a sleeping [[Mountain troll]] found just near the entrance to the [[Troll Stronghold (location)|Troll Stronghold]]. He currently seems to have no use in the game. There is a [[treasure trail]] clue which leads to coordinates just next to this troll. The player can hear a snoring sound if they stand near Mushroom.

Trolls are named after the first thing they eat or try to eat, so he must have eaten a [[mushroom]].

